#169
Road to Keep~
The cobblestone road widens here as it approaches the imposing silhouette of
the Wizard's Keep ahead. Worn ruts in the stone speak of heavy cart traffic
over many years. A weathered signpost points northward toward the keep's outer
gate, while narrower tracks branch east and west around the moat's perimeter.
The air smells faintly of woodsmoke and wet stone.
