#188
South Moat Path~
The moat path continues south of the keep. A drainage gutter runs alongside
the path here, filled with murky runoff from the keep above. The stench is
considerable. Moss-covered stones make the footing uncertain; more than one
careless wanderer has gone over the edge. The far corner of the keep is now
visible to the east.
