#202
Hermit's Track~
A narrow, overgrown track branches off from the main path and winds into the
shadows of the forest. Old rubbish has been kicked to the sides, and a
battered wooden sign hangs from a tree, reading "Keep Out" in uneven letters.
Despite the warning, footprints in the soft earth suggest the hermit himself
passes this way frequently. The smell of damp leaves and old pipe smoke
lingers here.
