#203
Gate of the Wizard's Keep~
To the north, a large gate can be seen in front of the Wizard's Keep. It is a
double-sided gate made of strong oak wood, banded by mithril. The path towards
the gate is kept very clean, the cobblestones almost shining brightly in the
sun.
