#204
Courtyard - South Gate~
The inner side of the great gate opens onto a wide, flagstone courtyard. A
guardhouse stands to the east, and a matching one to the west, each with
arrow slits facing into the yard. The cobblestones here are scrubbed clean
and well-maintained. A pair of iron torch holders flank the gate, currently
unlit in the daylight. The smell of horses and fresh hay drifts from
somewhere nearby.
