#205
Courtyard - East Wing~
The eastern section of the courtyard stretches alongside the keep's outer
wall. A row of practice dummies stands against the wall, some showing recent
signs of use. Weapon racks line the wall nearby, mostly empty but for a few
spare spears. The eastern guard tower rises above, its door set into the base
of the wall. A guardsman walks this section of the yard with practiced ease.
