Courtyard - West Wing~
The western section of the courtyard mirrors the east, though it is given
over more to storage. Barrels of salted provisions and crates of firewood are
stacked neatly against the keep wall. A well has been dug here, its stone lip
worn smooth from years of use. The western guard tower entrance is visible in
the wall to the north. Drudges can be seen going about their chores.
