Courtyard - Central North~
The broad central expanse of the courtyard is dominated by a large stone
fountain, though the water has been drained for the season and its basin is
dry. Carved keep insignia adorn the fountain's sides. The main keep entrance
is visible to the north, its heavy oak door banded in black iron. Guards
patrol this central area vigilantly, and their eyes miss little.
