Courtyard - North Approach~
The northernmost section of the courtyard leads directly to the great keep
doors. Wide stone steps rise to a pair of heavy iron-banded doors that stand
partially ajar. Torches blaze in iron brackets to either side, their flames
guttering in the courtyard breeze. Moss grows in the cracks between the
stones. Sentinels stand watch here, their faces impassive under their helms.
