#217
Entrance to the Wizard's Keep~
The grand entrance to the Wizard's Keep is an imposing space. Carved stone
columns rise to a vaulted ceiling painted in faded celestial motifs — stars,
moons, and the symbols of arcane schools. The double doors behind you are
heavy iron-banded oak; ahead, another set of doors leads deeper into the
keep. Stone braziers hold magical flames that burn without fuel, casting a
cold blue-white light. Keep sentinels flank the inner doors, their eyes
following your every move.
