#220
Rotunda - West Alcove~
A curved alcove opens off the rotunda's western wall. Stone shelves hold
dozens of sealed clay jars, each labeled in a cramped arcane script. Tall
candlestands cast a warm, flickering glow over reading lecterns piled with
open books. A wizard's apprentice sits cross-legged on the floor, surrounded
by scattered manuscripts, muttering softly to herself as she studies. The
smell of candle wax and old ink fills the alcove.
