#221
Rotunda - South Passage~
A south-running passage branches off from the rotunda, its walls lined with
framed maps and diagrams of magical phenomena. Glass cases contain unusual
specimens — preserved creatures, crystallised magical energies, and curios
from distant places. Floating magelight globes trail along the ceiling at
head height, brightening as you approach and dimming behind you. The passage
feels watched, as if the artifacts themselves take note of passersby.
