#222
Rotunda - East Alcove~
The eastern alcove of the rotunda holds a collection of magical instruments
on padded tables: astrolabes, resonance forks, lens assemblies, and devices
of unknown purpose. Everything is neatly labeled and arranged. A keep scholar
moves quietly among the instruments, making notes on a wax tablet. He glances
up at your entry and returns to his work without a word. The smell of metal
polish and ozone is noticeable.
