#226
Basement - Main Corridor~
The main corridor of the basement runs east-west, lit by iron-bracketed
torches that smoke heavily due to poor ventilation. The floor is rough
undressed stone, damp underfoot. Side passages branch to the north and south.
Barrels and locked chests line the walls in neat rows, each stenciled with
inventory marks. The distant sound of dripping water echoes from somewhere
deeper. A faint chill emanates from the eastern passage.
