#232
Grand Foyer~
The grand foyer of the Wizard's Keep is a sprawling, high-ceilinged hall
that serves as the keep's main gathering and circulation space. Marble
columns rise to a painted vault overhead, depicting scenes of arcane
achievement. The floor is a complex geometric mosaic in black and white
stone. Corridors and doors lead in every direction, and the hum of activity
fills the air. Keep drudges move through with purpose, and guards patrol the
perimeter with steady attention.
