#233
Foyer - Central Hall~
The central hall of the grand foyer is the keep's busiest thoroughfare.
Servants carry trays and bundles in every direction. A message board on the
wall near the north corridor is dense with pinned notes and duty rosters.
Wide doors to the east and west lead to the foyer's side wings. The smell
of warm food wafts from somewhere to the north, and the sound of animated
discussion echoes from the east wing.
