#235
Foyer - North Corridor~
The northernmost foyer corridor ends at a heavy locked door bearing a complex
brass mechanism. The door is clearly of high quality — no gaps at the edges,
no hinges visible, the lock plate engraved with magical seals. A notice
beside the door in formal script reads "Inner Keep: Authorised Entry Only."
The air here is noticeably still, as though sound and movement are muffled
by some ward. Even the torches burn without flickering.
