Foyer Lobby - East Passage~
The east passage of the foyer lobby connects the north and south wings of
the keep's public areas. Long display cases line the walls here, containing
artifacts of the keep's history — old weapons, fragments of spell-inscribed
stone, and sealed vials of unidentified liquids. Each case is secured with
a fine lock. The floor here is swept clean, and the lighting is brighter
than elsewhere, the better to display the collection.
