Foyer Lobby - South East~
The south-east corner of the foyer lobby connects the main foyer to the
east wing and back through the south archway. A large decorative tapestry
hangs here, depicting the founding of the Wizard's Keep in vivid colours —
though several sections have been repaired or patched, changing the original
scene in subtle ways. A plain wooden chair beneath the tapestry is occupied
by a guard leaning on a spear, watching the passage with half-lidded eyes.
