#245
Secret Passageway - Entrance~
A hidden door in the foyer's west wing opens onto a narrow passage that
clearly was not part of the keep's original construction. The walls are rough
and the ceiling low, forcing a stoop. Cobwebs thick with dust suggest this
passage has not been used in some time, yet the floor shows faint tracks in
the grime. A smell of old mortar and something damp hangs in the close air.
A torch bracket holds an old stub, long since burned out.
