#255
Secret Passageway~
The narrow hidden passage continues, curving gently to follow the line of
the keep's outer wall. The gap between the keep's double walls is barely
wide enough to walk without turning sideways. Rough iron spikes have been
driven into the wall at shoulder height, perhaps as handholds or perhaps as
crude weapons storage. Old scraps of cloth and a broken lantern suggest
someone sheltered here once. The silence is absolute.
