#256
Secret Passageway~
A section of the hidden passage widens slightly where the inner and outer
walls do not perfectly align. A low alcove has been hollowed out of one
wall, just large enough to crouch inside. Old candle stubs cluster in the
alcove, and rough marks on the stone above them look like a tally — someone
counting days. The thought is not a comfortable one. The passage continues
north and south through the keep's hidden spaces.
