#257
Secret Passageway - Descending~
The secret passage dips sharply downward here, a rough stair of uneven
stone treads leading down into a deeper, older space. The walls become raw
bedrock. The air is damper, the smell of earth and old magic strong. At the
base of the stairs below, a faint light can be seen — not torchlight, but a
steady pale glow from some unseen source. Faint sounds that might be whispers
reach your ears, then stop when you hold still.
