#258
Secret Chamber~
A hidden chamber cut from the bedrock beneath the keep. The pale light
comes from runes carved floor to ceiling across every surface, still
active after who knows how many decades. In the centre of the room, a stone
dais holds a locked iron chest, its lock mechanism arcane in design. The
air hums with suppressed power. Sitting before the chest, as though he has
been expecting you, is an aged figure in grey robes — the Master Archivist,
sworn guardian of the keep's most dangerous secrets. His eyes open slowly,
and he does not look surprised to see you here.
~
